description: The boys insight some serious controversy as they pick apart several "Cigar of the Year lists. Plus they unveil the results of their "Match Stick Poll" for the New Hampshire Republican Primary. Musical Chairs? Mr. Johnathan admits to participating in underground musical chairs and talks about his world ranking.
